              "text_evidence": "We came in peace for all mankind.",
              "read_aloud": "Excerpt. We came in peace for all mankind. If you could add one more sentence to the plaque, which idea would best match the message? A. “This journey belongs to all people on Earth.” B. “Only astronauts should explore space.” C. “The Moon belongs to one nation forever.” D. “Space travel should end now.”",
