              "source_question_no": 23,
              "type": "multiple_choice",
              "assessment_type": "level",
              "level": 10,
              "category": "Comprehension - Create",
              "focus": "create",
              "difficulty_band": "mastery",
              "excerpt": "I could see Earth, our home, in the sky overhead-blue water, white clouds, and brown land. I could see the continents, and I knew that they were younger than the Moon dust in which Neil and I were now leaving our footprints.",
              "stem": "If you could leave a message on the Moon for people on Earth, what would you write and why?",
