          "rationale": "While independence and confidence were important, determination appears throughout Buzz's story: holding onto his rocks, surviving West Point, applying again to the astronaut program, and meeting every challenge of the Moon mission. The text says he \"struggled to learn, to compete, to succeed\" and \"didn't give up.\" Determination was the key quality that kept him going through every obstacle.",
